newmonster "Hellgate Guard"
spr1 "./sprites/hellgateguard01.tga"
spr2 "./sprites/hellgateguard02.tga"
descr "The Gates of Inferno are the gates of a prison, nobody with a remaining spark of sanity would want to enter, and every waking thought is one of escape. Holding these livid hordes at bay during any contact between our worlds is the duty of the Hellgate Guard. Chosen champions fused into an armor of living metal, bestowed with weapons forged from fallen stars and a drop of angel's blood. During their training the mind of the guard-to-be is banished into the shadows of the demon realm, meant to endure every kind of suffering known - and yet unknown - to mankind. Those who return gained intimate knowledge of their prey, numb and hollow on the inside, unimpressed even by the most gruesome of sights. But most do never return, their soul now part of the raging masses, storming the iron gates, thrown back by the unyielding shields of their former brothers."
